{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/announcements/2017/06/23/announcing-angular-master-class-in-houston.html","webpackCompilationHash":"0c5d630095500f933ccd","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Articles by thoughtram","authors":[{"id":"pascal_precht","name":"Pascal Precht","twitter":"PascalPrecht","img":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/445106?s=460&v=4"},{"id":"christoph_burgdorf","name":"Christoph Burgdorf","twitter":"cburgdorf","img":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/521109?s=460&v=4"},{"id":"dominic_elm","name":"Dominic Elm","twitter":"d3lm","img":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/12571019?s=400&v=4"},{"id":"thomas_burleson","name":"Thomas Burleson","twitter":"thomasburleson","img":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/210413?s=400&v=4"},{"id":"elvira_eulitz","name":"Elvira Eulitz","twitter":"ElviraEulitz","img":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/29247040?s=400&v=4"},{"id":"maxim_koretskyi","name":"Maxim Koretskyi","twitter":"maxim_koretskyi","img":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/6124091?s=400&v=4"}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"483915b1-6183-517a-a7d7-1faadf91bbea","excerpt":"Angular Master-Class Training It’s been almost 7 months since our last AMC training in USA: \nBrooklyn, NY.   With help from Bonnie Brennan Angular Meetup…","html":"<h3>Angular Master-Class Training</h3>\n<p>It’s been almost 7 months since our last AMC training in USA:\n<a href=\"https://blog.thoughtram.io/announcements/2016/08/30/announcing-angular-2-master-class-in-nyc.html\">Brooklyn, NY</a>.  </p>\n<p>With help from Bonnie Brennan <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/ngHouston/\">Angular Meetup Houston</a>, we are very pleased to announce that our\nAngular Master Class is finally coming to <strong>Houston, Texas</strong> on <strong>August 22 - 25, 2017!</strong> </p>\n<p>And we found the perfect, artsy venue: Bisong Art Gallery, Houston Texas. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3cbfe4eeb88d4504ea33bfadf67e8962/d1d06/amc_houston_hall2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.77777777777778%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"amc houston hall2\"\n        title=\"amc houston hall2\"\n        src=\"/static/3cbfe4eeb88d4504ea33bfadf67e8962/a296c/amc_houston_hall2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3cbfe4eeb88d4504ea33bfadf67e8962/f544b/amc_houston_hall2.jpg 200w,\n/static/3cbfe4eeb88d4504ea33bfadf67e8962/41689/amc_houston_hall2.jpg 400w,\n/static/3cbfe4eeb88d4504ea33bfadf67e8962/a296c/amc_houston_hall2.jpg 800w,\n/static/3cbfe4eeb88d4504ea33bfadf67e8962/d1d06/amc_houston_hall2.jpg 1044w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>After all, fun places are sure to get everyone into the right state of mind to learn the\nnuances and power of Angular!</p>\n<h3>About the Training</h3>\n<p>You or your team should attend our 4-day <strong>Angular Master Class</strong> training.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Developers should note that this is the first time we have offered a public <strong>4-day</strong> training!\nThe reason we added another day is because we want to teach our brand new course material focused on  <strong>Redux and ngrx</strong>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4>Training Schedule</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Day 1: Jump Start with full, high-level introduction to Angular</li>\n<li>Day 2: Observables &#x26; Component Architecture</li>\n<li>Day 3: Routing &#x26; Forms</li>\n<li>Day 4: Redux + ngrx with immutable, 1-way dataflows and reactive programming\n<img src=\"/images/ngrx_sample.jpg\" style=\"margin-top:15px; width:75%; margin-bottom:10px\" alt=\"Sample: ngRx Lab Exercise\"></li>\n</ul>\n<p>These are intense, full 8-hour days… but don’t worry, we make the classroom fun. thoughtram teaches the class with two (2) trainers. And almost every 30 minutes, students work with hands-on, coding lab exercises.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p> We have also updated our course and lab exercises to use Angular Material and Angular Flex-Layout. You can read about that here: <a href=\"https://blog.thoughtram.io/angular/2017/01/08/a-revamped-angular-master-class.html\">Revamped Angular Master Class</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>We also have social time after class on Day 2 and Day 4. Leverage the social times for networking, offline questions, and simply relaxing with your fellow Angular-philes.\nSo come to our training, have a blast, and get the best acceleration into Angular possible. </p>\n<h3>On-Premise, Private Training?</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/83cf5b835585bf37945ae0151a293ae1/22fa6/sample_private_training.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 76.66891436277815%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sample private training\"\n        title=\"sample private training\"\n        src=\"/static/83cf5b835585bf37945ae0151a293ae1/a296c/sample_private_training.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/83cf5b835585bf37945ae0151a293ae1/f544b/sample_private_training.jpg 200w,\n/static/83cf5b835585bf37945ae0151a293ae1/41689/sample_private_training.jpg 400w,\n/static/83cf5b835585bf37945ae0151a293ae1/a296c/sample_private_training.jpg 800w,\n/static/83cf5b835585bf37945ae0151a293ae1/c35de/sample_private_training.jpg 1200w,\n/static/83cf5b835585bf37945ae0151a293ae1/22fa6/sample_private_training.jpg 1483w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>If you prefer private, on-site training for your development teams [10 or more developers],\nplease contact us for rates, details, and scheduling: <a href=\"mailto:hello@thoughtram.io?subject=Re Private AMC Training\">hello@thoughtram.io</a></p>\n<h3>Tickets on sale now</h3>\n<p>You can find more information on our official <a href=\"https://amc-houston.eventbrite.com/?aff=blogAnnouncement\">event page</a>, or grab your public training ticket right here!</p>\n<iframe  src=\"//eventbrite.de/tickets-external?eid=35632678300&ref=etckt\" frameborder=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" marginheight=\"5\" marginwidth=\"5\" scrolling=\"auto\" allowtransparency=\"true\"></iframe>\n<p>See you in Houston!</p>","frontmatter":{"author":"christoph_burgdorf","title":"Announcing Angular Master Class in Houston","imageUrl":{"childImageSharp":{"sizes":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5110913930789707,"src":"/static/905bf8bf95b1f6b050df4ad790019843/30037/announcing_amc_houston.jpg","srcSet":"/static/905bf8bf95b1f6b050df4ad790019843/10bdc/announcing_amc_houston.jpg 158w,\n/static/905bf8bf95b1f6b050df4ad790019843/f4ab0/announcing_amc_houston.jpg 315w,\n/static/905bf8bf95b1f6b050df4ad790019843/30037/announcing_amc_houston.jpg 630w,\n/static/905bf8bf95b1f6b050df4ad790019843/9810d/announcing_amc_houston.jpg 945w,\n/static/905bf8bf95b1f6b050df4ad790019843/ff2e4/announcing_amc_houston.jpg 1260w,\n/static/905bf8bf95b1f6b050df4ad790019843/49524/announcing_amc_houston.jpg 3406w","sizes":"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px"}}},"date":"23 June 2017","summary":"Our Angular Master Class comes to Houston. Join us for four entire days full of fun and learning Angular!","categories":["announcements"]}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/announcements/2017/06/23/announcing-angular-master-class-in-houston.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/announcements/2017/06/23/announcing-angular-master-class-in-berlin.html"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2017/06/23","title":"Announcing Angular Master Class in Berlin","categories":["announcements"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/angular/2017/07/26/a-web-animations-deep-dive-with-angular.html"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2017/07/26","title":"A web animations deep dive with Angular","categories":["angular"]}}}}}